1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:12,000
(Watch on www.kisskh.li Support Admin)

2
00:01:05,958 --> 00:01:06,666
You just got here?

3
00:01:07,208 --> 00:01:09,041
Haven't seen you around before

4
00:01:10,208 --> 00:01:12,666
Yeah, arrived last night

5
00:01:15,083 --> 00:01:16,291
You're really beautiful

6
00:01:16,833 --> 00:01:18,041
Took my breath away

7
00:01:19,833 --> 00:01:20,625
You…

8
00:01:21,666 --> 00:01:23,041
You're handsome too

9
00:01:23,833 --> 00:01:24,666
Really

10
00:01:28,375 --> 00:01:29,166
Mm

11
00:01:37,666 --> 00:01:38,875
(sneeze)

12
00:01:39,750 --> 00:01:40,958
Sorry about that

13
00:01:46,916 --> 00:01:47,625
(blowing nose)

14
00:01:49,208 --> 00:01:50,791
Wow, you came prepared

15
00:01:53,041 --> 00:01:53,875
How about

16
00:01:54,833 --> 00:01:55,791
let's redo it?

17
00:01:55,833 --> 00:01:57,500
Sure, let's redo it

18
00:01:58,166 --> 00:01:58,958
Wait, wait

19
00:02:00,125 --> 00:02:04,000
This time, can you make it more… sensual?

20
00:02:49,875 --> 00:02:50,625
You just got here?

21
00:02:50,625 --> 00:02:52,041
Haven't seen you around

22
00:02:52,958 --> 00:02:56,458
Mm… care for a taste?

23
00:02:58,875 --> 00:03:00,750
Hey — what are you doing!

24
00:03:01,083 --> 00:03:02,708
You're the one who said "make it sensual"

25
00:03:02,958 --> 00:03:04,333
That's not what I meant

26
00:03:04,333 --> 00:03:05,666
That's harassment

27
00:03:05,666 --> 00:03:06,958
Harassment, my ass

28
00:03:07,291 --> 00:03:08,666
Sensual is exactly this

29
00:03:08,666 --> 00:03:10,000
Even if it's a fling

30
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,833
you don't just kiss right off the bat

31
00:03:11,833 --> 00:03:13,250
Forget it, I'm done acting

32
00:03:13,250 --> 00:03:14,291
I'll just go for it

33
00:03:15,875 --> 00:03:17,166
Are you out of your mind?!

34
00:03:17,166 --> 00:03:18,708
Out of my mind, what?

35
00:03:18,875 --> 00:03:20,916
Such a hassle — fine, if you don't want to

36
00:03:21,291 --> 00:03:22,666
Out of your mind

37
00:03:22,958 --> 00:03:23,791
Hmph

38
00:03:40,708 --> 00:03:42,416
You're the one who said it

39
00:03:42,666 --> 00:03:45,666
that changing locations would bring back the spark

40
00:03:46,041 --> 00:03:46,958
Now what?

41
00:03:46,958 --> 00:03:48,666
What do you mean "I said"?

42
00:03:48,833 --> 00:03:50,791
This is about both of us

43
00:03:50,833 --> 00:03:52,583
Shouldn't you be trying too?

44
00:03:54,208 --> 00:03:56,041
I've been doing my part

45
00:03:56,041 --> 00:03:57,458
Playing along with the meet-cute

46
00:03:57,458 --> 00:03:58,666
the first-love pretend

47
00:03:58,708 --> 00:03:59,041
and—

48
00:03:59,041 --> 00:04:00,916
Don't even talk about your bad acting

49
00:04:00,916 --> 00:04:02,333
You even got the book wrong

50
00:04:02,333 --> 00:04:03,750
Bringing an old classic

51
00:04:03,875 --> 00:04:06,083
This is 21st-century Lijiang

52
00:04:06,083 --> 00:04:07,041
People who don't know

53
00:04:07,041 --> 00:04:08,875
would think you're acting in Plum in the Golden Vase

54
00:04:10,875 --> 00:04:12,458
I really can't take you anymore

55
00:04:13,208 --> 00:04:14,250
I'm done talking

56
00:04:14,583 --> 00:04:15,625
Annoying

57
00:04:54,125 --> 00:04:55,583
What happened to us?

58
00:04:59,708 --> 00:05:00,791
Ask yourself

59
00:05:02,166 --> 00:05:04,750
This isn't making love anymore

60
00:05:06,333 --> 00:05:07,333
It's making hate

61
00:05:07,916 --> 00:05:09,000
Making hate?

62
00:05:10,333 --> 00:05:11,125
Yeah

63
00:05:16,583 --> 00:05:18,750
You don't even want to do it, do you?

64
00:05:18,916 --> 00:05:21,000
How long has it been?

65
00:05:27,208 --> 00:05:28,500
Say something, damn it

66
00:05:33,500 --> 00:05:35,375
Do you know that feeling?

67
00:05:37,125 --> 00:05:38,458
Even when I'm holding you

68
00:05:40,875 --> 00:05:42,083
I feel like

69
00:05:42,875 --> 00:05:45,333
none of you belongs to me anymore

70
00:05:49,916 --> 00:05:51,833
Do you understand that feeling?

71
00:06:45,875 --> 00:06:46,833
What are you looking at?

72
00:06:52,708 --> 00:06:53,666
So rude

73
00:07:12,500 --> 00:07:15,625
This glass sways with a heartless light~♪

74
00:07:15,666 --> 00:07:18,416
A toast to old debts of foolish love~♪

75
00:07:18,416 --> 00:07:21,166
Lijiang's night, I sing alone~♪

76
00:07:21,166 --> 00:07:23,916
Hoarse voice can't reach the gentle land~♪

77
00:07:24,291 --> 00:07:27,041
Then you push the door, fragrance trailing~♪

78
00:07:27,125 --> 00:07:29,875
A key that opens the wall of my heart~♪

79
00:07:29,916 --> 00:07:32,583
Eyes meet, sparking and crackling~♪

80
00:07:32,583 --> 00:07:35,250
This ruin suddenly bathed in moonlight~♪

81
00:07:35,708 --> 00:07:38,708
Get drunk! Get lost! Just for tonight!~♪

82
00:07:38,708 --> 00:07:41,208
Who cares about tomorrow, who's beside whom~♪

83
00:07:41,375 --> 00:07:44,458
Your gaze is just a temporary painkiller~♪

84
00:07:44,458 --> 00:07:46,958
My desolation is your playground~♪

85
00:07:47,208 --> 00:07:50,416
Get drunk! Get lost! Just for tonight!~♪

86
00:08:09,875 --> 00:08:11,041
So it really is you

87
00:08:11,916 --> 00:08:12,708
Yeah

88
00:08:13,500 --> 00:08:14,958
How'd you know I was at this table

89
00:08:15,666 --> 00:08:17,625
Huh? This is your table?

90
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:19,416
Mm

91
00:08:20,958 --> 00:08:21,375
Oh

92
00:08:21,791 --> 00:08:22,916
What a coincidence

93
00:08:26,750 --> 00:08:28,875
Looks like we're fated

94
00:08:29,958 --> 00:08:30,750
Yeah

95
00:08:30,750 --> 00:08:33,625
Hey, you sang really well

96
00:08:33,625 --> 00:08:35,208
Are you the resident singer?

97
00:08:35,208 --> 00:08:38,166
No, anyone drinking here can sing

98
00:08:38,500 --> 00:08:39,625
600 yuan a song

99
00:08:43,416 --> 00:08:44,250
Wanna sing?

100
00:08:44,250 --> 00:08:45,166
I'll request one for you

101
00:08:45,166 --> 00:08:47,166
No no, let's just drink

102
00:08:48,625 --> 00:08:49,291
Alright

103
00:09:00,333 --> 00:09:02,541
Hey, that song

104
00:09:02,916 --> 00:09:04,666
the last one you sang

105
00:09:05,416 --> 00:09:06,541
what was it called?

106
00:09:07,291 --> 00:09:09,750
Ah, that one

107
00:09:10,708 --> 00:09:12,625
"Love at the Corner"

108
00:09:12,875 --> 00:09:15,875
Bullshit, what corner

109
00:09:16,041 --> 00:09:17,208
There's no such song

110
00:09:17,583 --> 00:09:18,500
There isn't?

111
00:09:19,083 --> 00:09:20,625
Definitely not

112
00:09:20,625 --> 00:09:22,791
That song hasn't even been written yet

113
00:09:23,333 --> 00:09:24,708
You're making it up

114
00:09:25,291 --> 00:09:26,333
Am I?

115
00:09:27,208 --> 00:09:28,375
Definitely

116
00:09:28,916 --> 00:09:30,875
Then you write it

117
00:09:31,041 --> 00:09:32,250
Mm

118
00:09:32,250 --> 00:09:33,375
That song

119
00:09:33,791 --> 00:09:34,916
write it now

120
00:09:35,041 --> 00:09:38,833
Come on, I can't write songs

121
00:09:38,875 --> 00:09:40,375
I only sing them

122
00:09:41,791 --> 00:09:42,916
Whatever, you

123
00:09:45,041 --> 00:09:45,833
Mm

124
00:09:46,375 --> 00:09:48,833
My drink's empty — give me yours

125
00:09:51,208 --> 00:09:52,250
Hey, you—

126
00:09:57,291 --> 00:09:58,833
Mine's gone too

127
00:10:00,958 --> 00:10:02,750
So, want to keep drinking?

128
00:10:02,833 --> 00:10:03,458
Mm

129
00:10:03,666 --> 00:10:04,750
Then next round

130
00:10:05,541 --> 00:10:06,333
Hm?

131
00:10:07,041 --> 00:10:07,833
Hey

132
00:10:08,583 --> 00:10:11,083
You keep showing up in my line of sight

133
00:10:11,458 --> 00:10:13,791
Are you into me or something?

134
00:10:16,500 --> 00:10:17,333
Hey

135
00:10:17,875 --> 00:10:20,458
You're the one who keeps showing up in mine

136
00:10:21,208 --> 00:10:22,750
And you said it yourself

137
00:10:23,250 --> 00:10:24,666
it's all coincidence

138
00:10:25,416 --> 00:10:27,958
I just happened to pick a song

139
00:10:28,375 --> 00:10:29,458
and you walked in

140
00:10:30,208 --> 00:10:31,416
And then…

141
00:10:35,333 --> 00:10:37,833
Sorry — accident

142
00:10:41,458 --> 00:10:43,083
You're so accident-prone

143
00:10:43,875 --> 00:10:45,875
Could you be a little more accident-prone? Hm?

144
00:10:48,833 --> 00:10:51,125
I think I'm sobering up

145
00:10:52,208 --> 00:10:53,833
If you wait too long

146
00:10:54,125 --> 00:10:56,125
my morals will sober up too

147
00:10:56,541 --> 00:10:58,583
Better hurry up

148
00:12:12,375 --> 00:12:14,333
That isn't your boyfriend's name, is it?

149
00:12:16,166 --> 00:12:16,791
Mm

150
00:12:24,166 --> 00:12:25,375
Forget him, just for now

151
00:12:37,500 --> 00:12:38,333
Nick

152
00:12:40,250 --> 00:12:41,041
I, um

153
00:12:41,791 --> 00:12:42,583
I—

154
00:12:53,583 --> 00:12:54,375
Hey

155
00:12:55,666 --> 00:12:56,458
You okay?

156
00:12:56,666 --> 00:12:57,458
You okay?

157
00:13:00,708 --> 00:13:01,500
You alright?
